01:02:15.031 --> 01:02:16.898
Tobias.

01:02:16.900 --> 01:02:19.401
Look here. Look here.

01:02:36.019 --> 01:02:38.019
I'm not sure I understand

01:02:38.021 --> 01:02:39.788
