standard margin.

01:38:07.281 --> 01:38:09.949
How do you feel?

01:38:14.054 --> 01:38:15.989
I think numbers don't lie.

01:38:15.991 --> 01:38:19.425
I didn't ask what you think;
I asked what you feel.

01:38:21.028 --> 01:38:24.297
I feel...

01:38:24.299 --> 01:38:26.399
